      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes how "http" URIs can be accessed using Transport Layer Security (TLS) and HTTP/2 to mitigate pervasive monitoring attacks.  This mechanism not a replacement for "https" URIs; it is vulnerable to active attacks.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
